OL,6,FThere's concern that 400 members of
OL,7,Fstaff could lose their jobs at Cardiff
OL,8,FUniversity.
OL,10,FThe Vice Chancellor has announced that
OL,11,F"difficult decisions" need to be taken
OL,12,Fwhich could also see school and
OL,13,Fsubject closures at Wales' largest
OL,14,Funiversity.
OL,16,FVice-Chancellor Professor Wendy Larner
OL,17,Fhas proposed that the university will
OL,18,Fno longer provide courses in Ancient
OL,19,FHistory, Modern Languages and
OL,20,FTranslation, Music, Nursing, and
OL,21,FReligion and Theology.
